			<div class="thumb" style="width: 210px;"><div style="margin:37.5px auto;"><a href="/wiki/%D0%A4%D0%B0%D0%B9%D0%BB:Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg/180px-Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg" decoding="async" width="180" height="135" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg/270px-Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5e/Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg/360px-Shevchenko%27s_gravestone_in_Saint_Petersburg.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4000" data-file-height="3000" /></a></div></div>
